{"tid":2327510,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺啲餐廳要求員工憑記憶落單好on9","createTime":"2020-12-16T06:07:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T09:01:46.000Z","uid":71237,"like":76,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ea009de15b245d06cc9cf1dce03b2b9cd16732cd","tid":2327510,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:07:00.000Z","msg":"幾年前去一間西餐廳食嘢，嗰度啲員工都係憑記憶落單。即係佢地唔會抄低你食咩 / 搵部iPad同你落單，而係記低order之後再去搵部機篤篤篤。<br />\n嗰次個侍應直頭漏咗我張單，最後等咗成粒鐘先有嘢食。<br />\n<br />\n老老實實，我情願侍應即時抄低，好過憑記憶落單之後又漏單。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J3byTa3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ3byTa3.jpg&h=cd2061f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"424e1986f375ee815165a8bc04d36cc7a921683d","tid":2327510,"uid":139224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:39:34.000Z","msg":"咁撚on9？<br />\n可能我食開平嘢，未見識過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb116f79383944474e5db14389cd9cd8622ab01d","tid":2327510,"uid":71237,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:42:15.000Z","msg":"憑記憶落單依啲嘢一定係老細要求員工咁做，諗住刁難吓啲員工就好似高級啲。<br />\n老老實實，我落單你唔抄低我唔會覺得高級啲，反而你認真抄低或者即時iPad落單我先覺得尊重我。"},{"pid":"8acc8e2be49ba7839ddb6792fe2c836add516a3a","tid":2327510,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:57:09.000Z","msg":"其實用紙筆抄低都係易漏單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ff2f1ee44a52e9d2fab167e26c8794089bb220","tid":2327510,"uid":71237,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"424e1986f375ee815165a8bc04d36cc7a921683d","tid":2327510,"uid":139224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:39:34.000Z","msg":"咁撚on9？<br />\n可能我食開平嘢，未見識過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:52:03.000Z","msg":"有啲人真係覺得憑記憶落單高級啲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EZuD5cj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEZuD5cj.jpg&h=d316a8f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/review/%E9%A3%9F%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE%E5%90%8D%E6%B0%A3-e2755090\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.openrice.com%2Fzh%2Fhongkong%2Freview%2F%25E9%25A3%259F%25E8%25A3%259D%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%2590%258D%25E6%25B0%25A3-e2755090&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU%2FFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=48742ca7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/review/%E9%A3%9F%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE%E5%90%8D%E6%B0%A3-e2755090</a><br />\n<br />\n我自己就覺得侍應都係打份工，俾人地用紙筆輕鬆啲仲好啦。<br />\n正如有啲人見到保安有凳坐都會覺得佢地偷懶、唔專業。其實對人可以寬容啲，唔洗為咗滿足人地虛榮心而搞到人地咁辛苦。<br />\n（利申：我食嗰間唔係Amigo，只係普通西餐廳。）"},{"pid":"9950d3516fa3ca10fc4dff057491b4078be4e2f9","tid":2327510,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:53:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁撚on9？<br />\n可能我食開平嘢，未見識過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>有啲人真係覺得憑記憶落單高級啲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EZuD5cj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEZuD5cj.jpg&h=d316a8f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/review/%E9%A3%9F%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE%E5%90%8D%E6%B0%A3-e2755090\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.openrice.com%2Fzh%2Fhongkong%2Freview%2F%25E9%25A3%259F%25E8%25A3%259D%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%2590%258D%25E6%25B0%25A3-e2755090&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU%2FFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=48742ca7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/review/%E9%A3%9F%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE%E5%90%8D%E6%B0%A3-e2755090</a><br />\n<br />\n我自己就覺得侍應都係打份工，俾人地用紙筆輕鬆啲仲好啦。<br />\n正如有啲人見到保安有凳坐都會覺得佢地偷懶、唔專業。<br />\n其實對人可以寬容啲，唔洗為咗滿足<span class=\"red\">自己</span>虛榮心而搞到人地咁辛苦。<br />\n（利申：我食嗰間唔係Amigo，只係普通西餐廳。）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ntypo"},{"pid":"79776960497bd40c1290d5794e16b9b875af0aa0","tid":2327510,"uid":1788,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:5